===Noun===
'''moon''' (''plural'' '''[[moons]]''')

#<!--DefA-->(''often capitalized'') The sole natural [[satellite]] of the [[Earth]].
#<!--DefB-->Any substantially sized natural satellite of a planet.
#<!--DefC-->(''literary'') A month, particularly a lunar month.
#:''many moons ago''

